episodes.title: Is this a CULT? My time in Multi-Level Marketing || Intellectual Potluck Podcast
episodes.description:
Are MLMs really cults? And how do people get caught up in them? Join me as I dive into how people can end up in these situations, and the problematic side to girlbossing your way through life.
